{"tid":1013016,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟一齊討論下伊藤潤二","createTime":"2019-02-08T04:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T11:14:33.000Z","uid":52362,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ac969ed9ef2e8740394dd98e0a2d7b3a65a6c71c","tid":1013016,"uid":52362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:36:46.000Z","msg":"其實係我有野唔明想問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n富江嗰度<br />\n1）其實富江係唔係驚火？佢有兩集好似都有透露過火係可以收到富江皮<br />\n2）嗰個唔受富江誘惑嘅男人係咩事？點解佢有呢種能力？我有Google過下，但係網上好似冇咩人討論<br />\n3）富江同黑色精子邊個好打啲？<br />\n4）富江同一拳邊個好打啲？<br />\n5）諗到再問<br />\n<br />\n雙一嗰度<br />\n雙一整嘅鬼屋其實係唔係發夢？又殺晒佢全家，雙一唔似咁邪惡.....<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n你地有冇啲睇伊藤嘅心得可以分享下？<br />\n就好似之前我喺連登睇到<br />\n原來潰談（突然人體爆炸嗰集）係想將人類代入蚊個角色，講下蚊嘅無奈，唔可以唔吸血，身不由己，然後一但俾人發現就會隨時爆炸<br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8485d4c5908cd78ba993ae9c888c981b05b6a585","tid":1013016,"uid":111497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:43:42.000Z","msg":"變態的藝術~"},{"pid":"93debc1f99842ba21eb86b59247f3a31883c08f4","tid":1013016,"uid":78773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"一睇到富江同黑色精子邊個好打d就唔撚想再睇落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e447f12c2387b8104659696c316ef4c302253e1","tid":1013016,"uid":52362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93debc1f99842ba21eb86b59247f3a31883c08f4","tid":1013016,"uid":78773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"一睇到富江同黑色精子邊個好打d就唔撚想再睇落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話晒都動漫台"},{"pid":"902db2786469354bf61a797c866cd24d9d5b98c7","tid":1013016,"uid"